lead_paragraph: SUN CITY, South Africa - Alex Noren fired five birdies on the back nine to catapult the Swede into a two-shot lead at the halfway stage of the European Tour’s Nedbank Challenge on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Swede Noren Storms Into Sun City Lead With 67
